6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=x1cSpGFefnIQ7kNvgEPmIGe&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDxV5kfOWQ3yDn-3gnl481FP90XTE1QEdSg1KNymxG8gA&oe=671CE94E"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Cream Soda Club", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Gameplay\nWhenever your patrons have enjoyed the show, they \u2018like\u2019 your club. Spend likes as a resource to furnish and develop the venue, and make sure to create a unique atmosphere. Earn more likes to unlock more music tracks and customize your nightspot.\n\nKey features\n- Cream Soda tracks as game levels. Objects in the club react to the beat, turning the game into a music video. \n- Nightclub as the game world. Purchase and place disco balls, speakers, projectors, poufs, and other furnishings.\n- Patron is the law. Some want to dance, some want to eat, and others come to socialize. Your task is to cater to everyone\u2019s needs.\n- Interact with Cream Soda band members as game characters and upgrade their DJ equipment.\n- Sync up with Cream Soda\u2019s music!\n", "short_description": "Cream Soda Club transports you into the world of EDM and parties. Play as an event manager: furnish the club and throw parties with Cream Soda."}]}, "developer_name": "Cream Soda Club Team", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://itseven-studio.com/privacy_policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Cream Soda Club Team", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://itseven-studio.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "939033889924114"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": nu